content.p: Due to the current situation with the COVID-19 pandemic, the university has decided to have online examination. Please refer to Exams Office at Exams@nottingham.edu.my for further information. Please take note that University of Nottingham Malaysia (UNM) may operate a different approach to online exams depending on the local circumstances and operations.
